even for a moment.

590
00:24:51,720 --> 00:24:53,200
He doesn’t even think he was wrong.

591
00:24:55,760 --> 00:24:56,560
How can I forgive

592
00:24:57,080 --> 00:24:58,280
such a person?

593
00:25:01,480 --> 00:25:02,840
