669
00:28:39,320 --> 00:28:40,880
That’s how the world works.

670
00:28:41,520 --> 00:28:42,200
Zhiyou,

671
00:28:43,360 --> 00:28:45,400
do you really think

672
00:28:45,400 --> 00:28:47,200
Li Zhe’s father never deceived others?

673
