711
00:30:35,680 --> 00:30:37,360
There’s no way I’d apologize to

712
00:30:38,320 --> 00:30:39,320
Li Jinghong.

713
00:30:42,800 --> 00:30:43,640
I knew

714
00:30:44,400 --> 00:30:45,520
