739
00:32:38,640 --> 00:32:40,440
After you left home,

740
00:32:40,680 --> 00:32:41,280
dad never let me

741
00:32:41,280 --> 00:32:42,800
enter your room.

742
00:32:50,960 --> 00:32:51,920
How come your bed

743
00:32:51,920 --> 00:32:53,200
