Shiyu?

756
00:33:29,000 --> 00:33:29,760
Shiyu?

757
00:33:30,840 --> 00:33:32,040
Go back to your room to sleep.

758
00:33:32,920 --> 00:33:33,960
You’ve grown up.

759
